Senior legal and business professional with experience in corporate, international, licensing, patent and trademark law in Canada, Russia and USA. Expertise in department building and management, IP strategy, legal strategy, licensing, mediation, negotiations, patent/trademark prosecution, start-ups and technology transfer. 

